message.content:
There is a kitchen with a dining area. 
In the kitchen there are dark brown cupboards and a small countertop with a sink on the right. 
Above the countertop there is a brown vent cover. 
On the countertop are a stack of white plates, a jar with a red lid, a box of Jello, a box of Alpen Salt, a box of Rice Bubbles, another jar with a red and white lid, a yellow mug, a puzzle box with a Chucky on the cover and another box of Jello. 
There is a white fridge on the left. 
The dining area has a rectangular wooden table surrounded by white chairs. 
On the table is a puzzle box with a Chucky on the cover, a bottle of water, a white plate, a mug and 2 white cups stacked on each other. 
The floor is made of brown parquet. 
The walls are white. 
The kitchen and dining area share the same room. 
The room has a door. 
The kitchen has a stovetop.
